ANTI-PATTERNS (NEVER DO)
Starting work before checking SESSION.md for in-flight context Ending a session without writing to MEMORY.md (even "NGF" is a valid entry) Writing the same rule to multiple files (pick one location, per Memory Sync Rule) Skipping the build check and going straight to ADJOURNING on broken code 